Comment:	NEEM-2011-S1 CH4 outliers.
	Data points removed from dataset according to specified cut-off value.
	Please refer to Rhodes et al. (2013) for full discussion of origins outlying data points. 
	Briefly, these high frequency features are not artifacts of the continuous method and have been replicated by traditional discrete analyses. Comparison to chemistry measurements suggests they are related to biological in situ production of methane.
